lines.text: Now let me get this straight. You're telling me that these, these things are inside the Golden Gate Bridge, one. Two, that they only come out at night. And three, that they're responsible for the death of fifteen or more kids and three of my police officers?
Did you hear that sick sound?
Yeah, it was creepy. Probably your mom howling out her anti-sex warning.
Gook, slime... nobody knows yet. Forensics found it all around here.
